blueprint.label: Red Mall
blueprint.description:
This design is taken from
https://factorioprints.com/view/-M2ZjQ7ClF06M3fvp684
with the following modifications:
- updated for Factorio 2.x!
- use advanced oil processing
- autofill robot network
- add missing inserters for rail signals

Added extra concrete (x2):
https://www.reddit.com/r/factorio/comments/bb6bs0/updated_concrete_factory_i_made_for_you_guys/

entities.name: arithmetic-combinator
entities.player_description:
Calculate the average number of items per chest.
Using only the first car because a short-train could leave it empty while later cars make the station think it has capacity.

entities.name: decider-combinator
entities.player_description: Each requested item, as a flag.

entities.player_description: Add 1 before dividing by M to round-up.
